### 2. Shopping Cart Backend Integration
* **Cart Context ([userCartContext.jsx](file:///d:/Coding/HackOn/frontend/src/context/userCartContext.jsx))**: Replaced Firestore queries with async Axios requests to `GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/cart`. Implemented cart mutation methods to interact with backend endpoints:
  * `addToCartBackend(asin, quantity)`: Calls `POST /api/v1/cart/items`
  * `updateCartItemQtyBackend(asin, quantity)`: Calls `PUT /api/v1/cart/items/{asin}`
  * `deleteCartItemBackend(asin)`: Calls `DELETE /api/v1/cart/items/{asin}`
  * `clearCartBackend()`: Calls `DELETE /api/v1/cart`
* **Cart View UI ([CartItems.jsx](file:///d:/Coding/HackOn/frontend/src/components/cart/cartItems.jsx))**: Swapped direct Firestore updates in quantity handlers with context calls to `updateCartItemQtyBackend`, `deleteCartItemBackend`, and `addToCartBackend`.
* **Add to Cart ([Product.jsx](file:///d:/Coding/HackOn/frontend/src/components/products/Product.jsx) & [ProductDetails.jsx](file:///d:/Coding/HackOn/frontend/src/components/products/ProductDetails.jsx))**: Switched to posting additions directly to `/api/v1/cart/items`.

