* **Address Submission ([addressForm.jsx](file:///d:/Coding/HackOn/frontend/src/components/checkout/addressForm.jsx))**: Posted new addresses to `POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/addresses` instead of Firestore.
* **Address Selection & Deletion ([userAddresses.jsx](file:///d:/Coding/HackOn/frontend/src/components/checkout/userAddresses.jsx))**: Modified the delete click handler to send a request to `DELETE http://localhost:8000/api/v1/addresses/{address_id}` on the FastAPI backend.

